summary: This mod adds funny and interesting  weapon in The Elder of Scroll: Skyrim
descriptionHtml:
Behold the mighty Mughammer is appeared in frozen plains of Skyrim,claim it and destroy your enemies.This mod will add this strange and lovely creation of mine to your game,you can craft it on forge.
This is my first mod that i created and i am really pround with results i got.
author: Milos
